{"tid":786061,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【母性大發】營養不良B送院無人理 好心女警充當奶媽","createTime":"2018-08-19T16:23:19.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-20T11:16:53.000Z","uid":28765,"like":28,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"834c8df0f459e3fc2a6acc29a8238673ab641b2c","tid":786061,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T16:23:19.000Z","msg":"阿根廷一位女警在醫院當值時，見到一名男嬰哭個不停但無人理，母性大發下給肚餓男嬰餵哺母乳。<br />\n<br />\n阿雅拉（Celeste Ayala）在貝里索（Berisso）一間兒童醫院當值，見到送院男嬰營養不良，還有醫護人員形容他又臭又髒。阿雅拉見他嚎哭不停，但醫院職員又忙得無暇照顧他，於是親自餵他，哭聲亦遽然而止。<br />\n那男嬰的母親是單親媽媽，有五兄弟姊妹。<br />\n阿雅拉說，見到男嬰放手入口，知他一定是肚子餓，實在心中不忍，於是把他抱在懷中餵他。<br />\n阿雅拉的無私表現感動同袍埃雷迪亞（Marcos Heredia），拍下阿雅拉餵奶的圖片，在網上推許一番。<br />\n這幅令人感動的圖片，已獲至少12.8萬個讚。<br />\n英國《都市報》  <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180819/large/1534641107_ae82.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180819%2Flarge%2F1534641107_ae82.jpg&h=c37299e7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n阿雅拉不忍餓嬰嚎哭不停，親自餵他。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20180819/58581191\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180819%2F58581191&d=Na5T5XaPBVFKHouct36x3L%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=3ea8c22e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180819%2F58581191&h=905ccff1\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20180819/58581191</a><br />\n<br />\n我知會有咩留言<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7ef1343c97ced741d0242a9d80240ca57e3b3cf","tid":786061,"uid":20170,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"834c8df0f459e3fc2a6acc29a8238673ab641b2c","tid":786061,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T16:23:19.000Z","msg":"阿根廷一位女警在醫院當值時，見到一名男嬰哭個不停但無人理，母性大發下給肚餓男嬰餵哺母乳。<br />\n<b